data.description: Welcome to Unit 23B which was completely renovated in 2022! Stunning city & lake views from this Gold Coast, 23rd floor, 2 bed, 2.5 bath condo. Spacious open floor plan with floor to ceiling windows that boast sweeping views from every room! The home includes a fully integrated electronic and sound system, Herringbone wood flooring throughout, 65 canned lights, brand new dual zoned furnace and a/c units.The kitchen features Quartzite counter tops, brand new Viking appliances including a warming drawer in the double french oven, double sink, wet bar, double door wine and beverage cooler, instant hot water, a butler's pantry and a huge island. The bathrooms include Carrara marble with a smart toilet and dual shower heads in the main bathroom. The huge primary suite includes a sizable walk in closet and a private balcony. Brand new Miele washer and dryer in unit. The Carlyle offers the best in full service amenities including 24 hour door staff, valet parking, on site management and engineer. Rooftop Amenities include workout room, sundeck with grills, indoor swimming pool, beautiful ballroom connected to restaurant quality kitchen for entertaining and private parties. Located at the intersection of the Magnificent Mile & Oak Street in the heart of all that the Gold Coast has to offer! Additional valet parking is available starting at $245 per month. No pets or rentals permitted.
